    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "DHA JFK FC 1 / 79\nWELCOME\nWe welcome you on board our flight\nto the unitea states\nwith a traditional Arabic welcome of\nAHLAN WA SAHLAN\nHORS D'OEUVRE\nGulf Shrimps tastefully garnished\nand servea with a cocktail sauce\nSALAD\nSeasonal salad with a choice of Dressing\nENTERER\nROAS I SIRLOIN OF BEEF\nSucculent Sirloin Roasted and carved on board\nCHICKEN VALDOSTANA\nbreast or enIcren stutted win bruvere\nCheese in a rich cream sauce\nHAMOUR MEUNIERE PORTUGESE\nFillets of Hamour fried in butter and\ndressed on a spicy onion and tomato Sauce\nLAMB QOZI\nSliced Leg of Lamb served on a bed of Oriental rice\nEGETABLES\nRice - Ann Potatoes\nGreen Beans — Buttered Baby Carrots\nINTERNATIONAL CHEESE SERVICE\nOn the Cheese Board a selection of\nBlue Cheese - Gruyere - Edam - Camembert\naccompanied by an array of selected fresh fruit\nDESSERT\nChocolate Swiss Roll - Arabic Pastries\nFresh Coffee - Tea - Milk - Nescafe _ Soft Drinks — Fruit luice\nsaudia A Cognall"
